<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PT. Trimas Mitra Perkasa — Distributor Valve & Fitting Tepercaya</title>
    <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0f2d52;
            --primary-mid: #163d6e;
            --accent: #f47320;
            --accent-dark: #d4621a;
            --steel: #2a7ab8;
            --bg: #f0f4f8;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --text: #1e293b;
            --muted: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --radius: 12px;
        }
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-padding-top: 70px; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: var(--text); background: var(--surface); margin: 0; }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar { background: #fff !important; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0.7rem 0; }
        .nav-brand-name { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); line-height: 1.2; }
        .nav-brand-sub { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; }
        .nav-link { color: var(--muted) !important; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.5rem 0.9rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
        .nav-link:hover { color: var(--primary) !important; }
        .btn-portal { background: var(--accent); color: #fff !important; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.875rem; transition: all 0.2s; border: none; }
        .btn-portal:hover { background: var(--accent-dark) !important; transform: translateY(-1px); }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(140deg, #071929 0%, var(--primary) 50%, var(--primary-mid) 100%);
            padding: 5rem 0 4rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero::before {
            content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 50%, rgba(42,122,184,0.18) 0%, transparent 55%),
                              radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 15%, rgba(244,115,32,0.07) 0%, transparent 45%);
        }
        .hero-grid {
            position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0.03;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,1) 1px, transparent 1px),
                              linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 44px 44px;
        }
        .hero-tag {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
            background: rgba(244,115,32,0.12); color: #f9a05a;
            border: 1px solid rgba(244,115,32,0.25); border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .hero-title { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 3.1rem); font-weight: 800; color: #fff; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
        .hero-title .accent { color: #f9a05a; }
        .hero-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 540px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .btn-hero-primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem; font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .btn-hero-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-dark); color: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .btn-hero-outline { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .btn-hero-outline:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
        .hero-stats { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .hero-stat-val { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; line-height: 1; }
        .hero-stat-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 3px; font-weight: 500; }
        .hero-divider { width: 1px; height: 36px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }

        /* Cert bar */
        .cert-bar { background: #091e33; padding: 0.85rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
        .cert-pill { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.775rem; font-weight: 500; padding: 0.28rem 0.85rem; white-space: nowrap; }

        /* Sections */
        .section-eyebrow { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
        .section-h { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); line-height: 1.2; }
        .section-line { width: 44px; height: 3px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 2px; margin: 0.65rem 0 1rem; }

        /* About cards */
        .about-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.6rem; background: #fff; transition: all 0.3s; }
        .about-card:hover { border-color: var(--steel); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(15,45,82,0.09); transform: translateY(-4px); }
        .about-icon { width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.9rem; }

        /* Why us */
        .why-section { background: var(--primary); }
        .why-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.6rem; transition: all 0.3s; height: 100%; }
        .why-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.09); border-color: rgba(244,115,32,0.35); }
        .why-icon { width: 38px; height: 38px; background: rgba(244,115,32,0.12); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #f9a05a; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0.9rem; }

        /* Products */
        .product-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); background: #fff; transition: all 0.25s; overflow: hidden; height: 100%; }
        .product-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(15,45,82,0.1); transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: var(--steel); }
        .product-img-box { height: 155px; background: var(--bg); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 1rem; }
        .product-img-box img { max-height: 100%; max-width: 100%; object-fit: contain; }
        .btn-detail { display: block; width: 100%; background: transparent; border: 1.5px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .btn-detail:hover { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }

        /* CTA */
        .cta-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #071929 0%, var(--primary) 100%); border-radius: 16px; }
        .pdf-icon-circle { background: #fee2e2; color: #dc2626; width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.3rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .btn-dl { display: block; width: 100%; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .btn-dl:hover { background: var(--accent-dark); color: #fff; transform: translateY(-1px); }

        /* Footer */
        footer { background: #060e1a; color: #64748b; padding: 4rem 0 1.75rem; }
        .footer-link { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
        .footer-link:hover { color: #f9a05a; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg sticky-top shadow-sm">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center gap-2" href="/" style="text-decoration:none;">
            <img src="/logo.jpeg" alt="TMP Logo" style="height:38px;width:auto;border-radius:6px;">
            <div>
                <div class="nav-brand-name">PT. Trimas Mitra Perkasa</div>
                <div class="nav-brand-sub">Distributor Peralatan Industri · Batam</div>
            </div>
        </a>
        <!-- Portal button always visible on mobile, next to hamburger -->
        <a class="btn btn-portal d-lg-none me-2" href="/portal" style="font-size:0.8rem;padding:0.4rem 0.9rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket me-1"></i>Portal
        </a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler border-0 shadow-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navMain">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end gap-1" id="navMain">
            <ul class="navbar-nav align-items-lg-center mt-3 mt-lg-0">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#home">Beranda</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#about">Tentang Kami</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#products">Produk</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Kontak</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item ms-lg-3 mt-2 mt-lg-0 d-none d-lg-block">
                    <a class="btn btn-portal" href="/portal">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket me-2"></i>Portal Mitra
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<header id="home" class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid"></div>
    <div class="container position-relative">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <div class="hero-tag">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
                    Berbasis di Batam, Indonesia
                </div>
                <h1 class="hero-title">
                    Solusi Valve &amp; Fitting<br>
                    <span class="accent">Industri Terpercaya</span> di Batam
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-desc">
                    Menyediakan komponen industri berkualitas tinggi — valve, fitting, dan instrumen pipa — untuk kebutuhan sektor maritim, manufaktur, minyak &amp; gas, serta industri berat lainnya.
                </p>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <a href="#products" class="btn-hero-primary">
                        Lihat Produk Kami <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
                    </a>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-hero-outline" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#quoteModal">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice"></i> Minta Penawaran
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-stats">
                    <div class="hero-stat">
                        <div class="hero-stat-val">10+</div>
                        <div class="hero-stat-label">Tahun Pengalaman</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
                    <div class="hero-stat">
                        <div class="hero-stat-val">500+</div>
                        <div class="hero-stat-label">Klien Industri</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
                    <div class="hero-stat">
                        <div class="hero-stat-val">1000+</div>
                        <div class="hero-stat-label">SKU Produk</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- CERT BAR -->
<div class="cert-bar">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center gap-3">
            <span style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);white-space:nowrap;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved me-2" style="color:var(--accent);"></i>TERSERTIFIKASI
            </span>
            <span class="cert-pill">ISO 9001</span>
            <span class="cert-pill">ASME B16.5</span>
            <span class="cert-pill">API 600</span>
            <span class="cert-pill">SNI</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about" class="py-5" style="background:var(--bg);">
    <div class="container py-4">
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="section-eyebrow">Tentang Kami</div>
                <h2 class="section-h">Mitra Industri yang Dapat Anda Andalkan</h2>
                <div class="section-line"></div>
                <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;font-size:0.95rem;margin:0;">
                    PT Trimas Mitra Perkasa adalah distributor terkemuka di Batam yang berfokus pada penyediaan Valve, Fitting, dan instrumen pipa berkualitas tinggi. Kami melayani sektor maritim, manufaktur, migas, serta industri berat dengan standar internasional.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <div class="about-icon" style="background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8;"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
                    <h6 style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-size:0.975rem;">Resmi &amp; Bersertifikat</h6>
                    <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Terdaftar resmi sebagai PT (Perseroan Terbatas) dengan nomor registrasi 937987.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <div class="about-icon" style="background:#ffedd5;color:var(--accent);"><i class="fa-solid fa-truck-fast"></i></div>
                    <h6 style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-size:0.975rem;">Distribusi Cepat</h6>
                    <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Jaringan distribusi efisien dari Batam ke seluruh kota besar di Indonesia.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <div class="about-icon" style="background:#dcfce7;color:#16a34a;"><i class="fa-solid fa-award"></i></div>
                    <h6 style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-size:0.975rem;">Jaminan Kualitas</h6>
                    <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Produk premium memenuhi kualifikasi dan spesifikasi standar industri internasional.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <div class="about-icon" style="background:#ede9fe;color:#7c3aed;"><i class="fa-solid fa-users-gear"></i></div>
                    <h6 style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-size:0.975rem;">Dukungan Ahli</h6>
                    <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Tim profesional siap memberikan konsultasi teknis dan layanan pelanggan andal.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY US -->
<section class="why-section py-5">
    <div class="container py-4 text-center">
        <div class="section-eyebrow" style="color:rgba(249,160,90,0.75);">Keunggulan Kami</div>
        <h2 class="section-h mb-2" style="color:#fff;">Mengapa Memilih PT Trimas Mitra Perkasa?</h2>
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);font-size:0.9rem;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 3rem;">Mitra andal Anda untuk solusi valve dan fitting industri di seluruh Indonesia.</p>
        <div class="row g-4" style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="why-card text-start">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-box-open"></i></div>
                    <div style="font-weight:700;color:#fff;font-size:0.975rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Stok Ready di Batam</div>
                    <div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);font-size:0.855rem;line-height:1.65;">Produk tersedia langsung di gudang Batam, siap kirim ke seluruh Indonesia dengan waktu tunggu minimal.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="why-card text-start">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-medal"></i></div>
                    <div style="font-weight:700;color:#fff;font-size:0.975rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Material Berkualitas Tinggi</div>
                    <div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);font-size:0.855rem;line-height:1.65;">Tersedia dalam Stainless Steel SS316L, Carbon Steel, dan Duplex untuk berbagai aplikasi industri.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="why-card text-start">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i></div>
                    <div style="font-weight:700;color:#fff;font-size:0.975rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Harga Kompetitif</div>
                    <div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);font-size:0.855rem;line-height:1.65;">Penawaran langsung dari distributor — transparan, tanpa perantara, dengan diskon volume untuk order besar.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="why-card text-start">
                    <div class="why-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i></div>
                    <div style="font-weight:700;color:#fff;font-size:0.975rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Dukungan Teknis 24/7</div>
                    <div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);font-size:0.855rem;line-height:1.65;">Konsultan teknis berpengalaman siap membantu pemilihan spesifikasi material dan layanan purnajual.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- PRODUCTS -->
<section id="products" class="py-5" style="background:var(--bg);">
    <div class="container py-4">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between align-items-md-center mb-5 gap-3">
            <div>
                <div class="section-eyebrow">Katalog Produk</div>
                <h2 class="section-h">Produk Unggulan Kami</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="input-group" style="max-width:280px;">
                <span class="input-group-text bg-white border-end-0"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass text-muted" style="font-size:0.85rem;"></i></span>
                <input type="text" id="productSearch" class="form-control border-start-0 ps-0" placeholder="Cari produk..." style="font-size:0.875rem;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-4" id="productGrid">
            <% if (products && products.length > 0) { %>
                <% products.slice(0, 5).forEach(product => { %>
                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 product-item">
                        <div class="product-card">
                            <div class="product-img-box">
                                <% if (product.Img_Url) { %>
                                    <img src="/images/<%= encodeURIComponent(product.Img_Url) %>" alt="<%= product.Product_Name %>" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<i class=\'fa-solid fa-box\' style=\'font-size:3rem;color:#cbd5e1;\'></i>'">
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-box" style="font-size:3rem;color:#cbd5e1;"></i>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-4">
                                <span style="font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--steel);background:#dbeafe;border-radius:4px;padding:2px 8px;">PRODUK</span>
                                <h5 style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);margin:0.6rem 0 0.4rem;font-size:1.05rem;"><%= product.Product_Name %></h5>
                                <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:1.2rem;"><%= product.Short_Desc || 'Komponen industri berkualitas tinggi untuk kebutuhan perpipaan dan instrumentasi.' %></p>
                                <a href="/portal" class="btn-detail">Lihat Detail <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ms-2"></i></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } %>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                <div class="text-center p-3">
                    <div style="width:56px;height:56px;background:#dbeafe;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 0.9rem;font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--steel);"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
                    <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem;">Lebih banyak produk tersedia di katalog lengkap kami.</p>
                    <a href="/portal" class="btn-hero-primary" style="font-size:0.85rem;">Akses E-Katalog Lengkap</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA CATALOG -->
<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-box p-4 p-md-5 text-white">
            <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <span style="background:rgba(244,115,32,0.12);color:#f9a05a;border:1px solid rgba(244,115,32,0.25);border-radius:20px;font-size:0.775rem;font-weight:600;padding:0.3rem 0.9rem;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:1rem;">Panduan Produk Virtual</span>
                    <h2 style="font-size:1.9rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.75rem;line-height:1.2;">Unduh E-Katalog Produk Lengkap</h2>
                    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);line-height:1.75;max-width:500px;font-size:0.93rem;">Dapatkan akses instan ke seluruh daftar produk, spesifikasi teknis, dimensi, material, dan informasi harga — dalam satu dokumen PDF siap unduh.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:12px;padding:1.75rem;">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="pdf-icon-circle"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-pdf"></i></div>
                            <div>
                                <div style="font-weight:700;color:#fff;font-size:0.975rem;">E-Katalog Produk</div>
